Orangutang is not happy. It looked sad and tired of people knocking on the glass and waiving like ... well, apes.
Great place. Nice and quiet and good for a walk. Couples choose this place for wedding photoshoots, especially the part near Moroccan palace.
Dinner buffet is excellent. Wide choice of dishes, great bbq meat, lots of fruits and desserts. The only thing is the music - too loud, you can come back home with a headache.
The road to the top is actually more interesting, than the top itself. Wildlife is everywhere. Nice and quiet trip, loved this place most on Langkawi.
Suprised there were no visitors. The place is great! Lots of cute details, coffee art and, of course, racoons. Though, the food was not good, but the coffee and cheesecake were excellent.
